- "Bike type" includes different categories of bikes such as e-bikes or single bikes;
- "Average rental duration" is the mean time a bike is rented out;
- "Total maintenance cost" is the sum of all costs incurred in maintaining the bikes at a station.

- 'check-out' refers to the action of renting a bike from a station;
